Access Specifiers/Modifiers:
----------------------------
   These are keywords used to set the accessbilty or visiblity of class, variable, method and constructor.
public, protected, default, private

same class - visible in the class.
same package - Other classes in the same folder
Different package - folder1, folder2 - folder1 class is accessible in folder2 class.
Entire project. - Access from anywhere in the entire application.

Public 
--------
Access from anywhere. No restriction.

public class Student{
    public String name;
    public void printName(){
        sout("Name : "+ name);
    } 
}

Protected
----------

class Student{
    protected String name;
    protected void printName(){
        sout("Name : "+ name);
    } 
}


